Boxed In Privacy Policy
What Information We Collect
When you sign in to Apple or Facebook through Boxed In, we store your respective user id. This unique string of characters doesn't personally identify you, but allows us to associate you with high scores and level submissions.
How We Use Data We Collect
We use the your user id to indentify you as a person. This along with the user name you choose in Boxed In allows us to display player high scores in game and on the Boxed In website.
Who We Share Information With
We don't share your information with anyone.
How To Delete All Data Associated With Your Account
To request all data associated with your user id be deleted, please e-mail
myfriends@thepuzzleaisle.com